snippet.title: Big Time Early Access Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Early Access launches on April 19th.

Read our Medium article below for more information on the pass redemption process:
https://medium.com/playbigtime/early-access-passes-how-to-redeem-b94412bc07ba

If you own a Gold Pass, enter your onboarding here:
https://bigtime-21044391.hs-sites.com/gold-pass
